cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP address to an unreachable network (10.0.0.1) will cause the CU to fail in establishing connection to the AMF, leading to unreachable elements and service disruption.

du.explanation_en: Modifying the Ta4 timing parameters to inconsistent values will cause timing misalignment between the front-haul interface and the radio unit, resulting in synchronization failures and degraded performance.
